  <h2>One question before you leave</h2>
  <p class="sub">Unit-close reflection. Five minutes. This one matters — it's about how YOU think, not about the topic.</p>
  <div class="reflect-input">
    <strong>Prompt — metacognitive (process + tool use):</strong>
    <br>What AI tool helped you most in this dossier?
    <br>What did you do that was YOURS and not the AI's?
    <br>How would you describe that line to a parent — in 1-2 sentences they could understand without taking this class?
    <br><br>
    📝 Type your answer in your Reflection Journal, or 🎤 record a voice memo and drop it in your Drive folder.
